headline: RAD Intel CRO Emily Duban to Speak at The Next Revolution of AI: Impact Summit at Stanford
summary: SUNNYVALE, Calif., September 08, 2025--RAD Intel announced today that Chief Revenue Officer Emily Duban will speak at The Next Revolution of AI: Innovation Summit in Mountain View later today. This year’s prestigious program will convene leading voices in innovation to explore the next wave of applied AI, leadership, and real-world impact.
